SUMMARY:Information: Tottenham Hale Station: Beyonce Concerts at Tottenham 
 Hotspur Stadium on Saturday 7\, Tuesday 10\, Thursday 12\, Saturday 14 and
  Monday 16 June (1700 start): Tottenham Hale station is expected to be 
 extremely busy between 1530 and 1700 and between 2230 and 2355. You may 
 find it easier to use Northumberland Park station where additional Greater
  Anglia and Stansted Express trains will call before and after the match\,
  please board one of the front 7 coaches for Northumberland Park.
END:VEVENT
